    },
    {
      "key": "contribution.{57644AE6-7FFA-A231-8FE0-75-209500SOUBU}.description",
      "source": "旧式化した初期型103系置き換えのため登場。同線のE231とは前面が少し違う。",
      "translation": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "contribution.{57644AE6-7FFA-A231-8FE0-75-209500KEHIN}.name",
